OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy throughout
OL,6,Fthe day with showery outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, these turning heavy in places.
OL,8,FFeeling much cooler than recent days.
OL,9,FBreezy around the coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will remain cloudy through
OL,12,Fthe evening and overnight with some
OL,13,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, heavy at
OL,14,Ffirst, gradually easing overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FDull and cloudy through the
OL,17,Fmorning with a few light showers.
OL,18,FBrighter spells developing later in
OL,19,Fthe day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
