OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRain
OL,6,Ffor a time on Monday then bright
OL,7,Fspells and showers continuing through
OL,8,FTuesday and Wednesday. Remaining
OL,9,Fcooler with some overnight frost.
